The paper presents an approach for learning algorithms using neural networks, which suggests that it could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). The use of interfaces such as 1-D tapes and 2-D grids also suggests that it could be related to natural language processing (cs.CL) or computer vision (cs.CV).
